{
  "text": "(iii) IRE1 Pathway. The ER transmembrane protein inositol requiring kinase 1 (IRE1) regulates chaperone induction, ERAD, and expansion of the ER in response to ER stress [CITATION_1] . This pathway is highly conserved in evolution and is present in all eukaryotes.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "12249673"
